        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". It is quite true that Josephus says nothing directly of the Tyrians and Sidonians, but the audience was evidently granted to them on the second day of the public spectacle; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
